The highest price of Bitcoin in 2017 was reached on December 17, 2017, when the price of Bitcoin reached an all-time high of $19,783.06 USD according to CoinMarketCap. This marked a significant increase in the price of Bitcoin from the beginning of the year, when it was trading around $1,000 USD. The surge in the price of Bitcoin in late 2017 was driven by a combination of increasing demand, media attention, and speculation, but was followed by a significant market correction in the following year.